1.0.1.name: wordpress/zeebusiness
1.0.1.description: zeeBusiness is a two column wordpress theme in an elegant bold design with strong colors. It comes with three navigation menus (top, main and foot), five sidebar areas (blog, pages, 3x footer) and a Featured Posts Slider. You can choose between eleven color schemes or use the colorpicker to get every color you want. Other features are a Custom Logo Upload, 125x125 Banner Advertising Widget, SocialMedia Buttons Widget, Dropdown Navigation, Theme Option Panel, Threaded Comments, Sitemap Page Template, Slider Page Template and Fullwidth Page Template. Enjoy :)
